These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, sprite, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, rowing, golf, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
2. the person drinking soy-milk is not the person who's sport is climbing##6
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is not the person drinking sprite##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | iced-tea    | cola    | sprite |
| Sport      | snowboarding | climbing | golf | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, tea, water
There 4 different types of food: apple, garlic, pear, raspberry
1. the person eating apple is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
4. the person drinking fanta is not the person eating garlic##6
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating pear##1
7. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | fanta  | tea    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Food       | raspberry | garlic | pear  | apple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, soy-milk, milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, librarian, entrepreneur, social-worker
1. the person drinking milk is not the scientist##6
2. the librarian is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
3. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
4. the librarian is the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the librarian##1
6. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
7. the scientist is on the far left or far right##3
8. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of the social-worker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | milk       | tea  | juice  | soy-milk |
| Job        | entrepreneur | social-worker | librarian | scientist  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, rat, dog, bird
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, tram, motorbike, bike
1. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
3. the person driving the bike is not the owner of the rat##6
4. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
6. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | rat | dog | bird     | hamster |
| Transport   | tram     | motorbike    | car | bike    |

