.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, skateboard, taxi, roller
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
4. the person drinking cola is not the person driving the roller##6
5. the person driving the motorbike is not the person drinking coffee##6
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | coffee        | hot-chocolate | almond-milk | cola |
| Transport   | roller | motorbike | skateboard     | taxi   |

