.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, martial-arts, crime, adventure
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, dutch, nigerian, turkish
1. the mexican is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is not the dutch##6
3. the mexican is on the far right##1
4. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the turkish##5
5. the person watching crime movies is the person watching crime movies##1
6. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
7. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
9. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime    | time-travel  | adventure   |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | turkish | dutch | mexican |

