.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, fantasy, family, sports
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, soul, rock
1. the fan soul is on the left or right of the fan folk##3
2. the fan soul is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
3. the person watching scientific movies is the fan funk##1
4. the fan folk is on the left or right of the fan rock##3
5. the fan soul is on the far left##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is the fan folk##1
7. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the fan folk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | fantasy     | family | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | soul | folk | rock      | funk         |

