2. the chef is somewhere to the left of the writer##5
3. the chef is on the right of the manager##1
4. the manager is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
5. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the manager##3
6. the designer is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
7. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
8. the person drinking water is not the chef##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | water  | cola        | juice      | almond-milk          |
| Job        | designer | manager | chef | writer |

