.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, security-guard, firefighter, paramedic
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, bus, quad-bike, scooter
1. the designer is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bus is not the paramedic##6
3. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
4. the person driving the scooter is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
6. the person driving the scooter is the firefighter##1
7. the designer is not the person driving the scooter##6
8. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | designer  | firefighter | paramedic    | security-guard |
| Transport   | bus | scooter | quad-bike | snowmobile  |

