.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, cat, snake, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, cricket, basketball, badminton
1. the person who's sport is skiing is not the owner of the frog##6
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the owner of the snake is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
6. the person who's sport is cricket is not the owner of the cat##6
7. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the snake is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | snake | frog        | mouse  | cat     |
| Sport   | skiing     | badminton | cricket | basketball |

