.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, baking, gardening, camping
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, techno, classical, funk
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
2. the fan techno is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
3. the fan classical is not the person who's hobby is gardening##6
4. the person who's hobby is baking is between the fan funk and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the fan techno is between the fan blues and the person who's hobby is collecting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | gardening | baking    | collecting | camping |
| Music-Genre   | blues         | techno | funk   | classical     |

