.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, strawberry, peach, watermelon
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, taxi, boat, subway
1. the person eating peach is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
2. the person eating watermelon is not the person driving the ship##6
3. the person driving the taxi is the person eating watermelon##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person driving the boat is not the person eating watermelon##6
6. the person eating strawberry is not the person driving the ship##6
7. the person eating peach is somewhere to the left of the person eating strawberry##5
8. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | carrot  | peach | strawberry | watermelon |
| Transport   | boat | ship     | subway     | taxi    |

