The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, horror, disaster, animation
1. the person eating kale is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
2. the person eating peach is not the person watching horror movies##6
3. the person eating kale is the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
5. the person eating kale is between the person eating peach and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
6. the person eating peach is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | papaya | peach      | kale | artichoke   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror     | disaster | animation   | martial-arts |

