2. the person watching romance movies is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking soy-milk##2
4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | sprite       | soy-milk | cola     | mirinda     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | romance       | scientific | epic |

