.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, reading, photography
4 different pets are kept: rat, cat, hamster, goldfish
1. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
2. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6
5. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
8. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | chess | reading | card-games | photography |
| Pet     | hamster  | cat      | rat  | goldfish       |

