2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person driving the scooter is not the person drinking 7up##6
5. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
6. the person driving the van is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | 7up | coffee | sprite      | hot-chocolate   |
| Transport   | bus  | van   | tram | scooter |

 